cz.cvut.felk.cig.jcop.problem.sat
Class Clause

java.lang.Object
  cz.cvut.felk.cig.jcop.problem.sat.Clause

public class Clause
extends java.lang.Object

Part of Formula, contains negated and non-negated variables.

Formula consists of several clauses. Iff all clauses evaluates to true via isTrue(cz.cvut.felk.cig.jcop.problem.Configuration), then formula is evaluated to true as well.
